id="post-4014" class="post-4014 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-energy category-environment tag-coal tag-gas tag-germany tag-rwe tag-solar tag-wind"><h2 class="entry-title"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/2013/08/30/german-coal-and-gas-power-plants-closing-due-to-cheap-renewable-energy/" title="Permalink to German Coal and Gas Power Plants Closing Due to Cheap Renewable Energy" rel="bookmark">German Coal and Gas Power Plants Closing Due to Cheap Renewable Energy</a></h2><div
class="entry-meta"> <span
class="entry-date" title="2013/08/30 10:49 am"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/2013/08/30/german-coal-and-gas-power-plants-closing-due-to-cheap-renewable-energy/" title="German Coal and Gas Power Plants Closing Due to Cheap Renewable Energy" rel="bookmark">2013/08/30 10:49 am</a></span><span
class="entry-meta-sep"> / </span><span
class="entry-author author vcard"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/author/administrator/" title="by Adam Clare" rel="author">Adam Clare</a></span></div><div
class="entry-content clearfix"><p>Germany has been so effective in tranisitioning from unsustianble (econmically and environemntally) energy sources to renewable ones that it is uncompetitive to burn fossil fuels for power!</p><blockquote><p>&#8220;Due to the continuing boom in solar energy, many power stations throughout the sector and across Europe are no longer profitable to operate,&#8221; RWE said in a statement.</p><p>&#8220;During the first half of 2013, the conventional power generation division&#8217;s operating result fell by almost two-thirds. The massive reduction in power station margins is a major factor in this development.&#8221;</p><p>On Tuesday, E.On said it had shut down or left idle 6,500 megawatts of generating capacity.</p><p>It had previously announced plans to close a total of 11,000 megawatts, but now says it may close more.</p></blockquote><p><a
href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-23692530">Read more at the BBC.</a></p><div
class='sharedaddy sd-block sd-like jetpack-likes-widget-wrapper jetpack-likes-widget-unloaded' id='like-post-wrapper-1111807-4014-53835c40bd5cc' data-src='//widgets.wp.com/likes/#blog_id=1111807&amp;post_id=4014&amp;origin=www.thingsaregood.com&amp;obj_id=1111807-4014-53835c40bd5cc' data-name='like-post-frame-1111807-4014-53835c40bd5cc'><h3 class='sd-title'>Like this:</h3><div
